## Deploy Jira Connector

### Profile

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **nipyapi Profile** | `{{ nipyapi_profile }}` |

### CLI Commands

```bash
# List available connectors in the Snowflake registry
nipyapi --profile {{ nipyapi_profile }} ci list_flows

# Deploy the Jira Cloud connector
nipyapi --profile {{ nipyapi_profile }} ci deploy_flow \
  --bucket "Snowflake Openflow Connector Registry" \
  --flow "Jira Cloud"
```

> Capture the **process group ID** returned by `deploy_flow`. You will need it for the next two steps (configure parameters, enable controllers).
